/#
 A day type classification used in counting the number of days between two dates.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.DayTypeEnum {
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only business days.
    Business 
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes all calendar days.
    Calendar 
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only commodity business days.
    CommodityBusiness 
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only currency business days.
    CurrencyBusiness 
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only stock exchange business days.
    ExchangeBusiness 
    # When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only scheduled trading days.
    ScheduledTradingDay 

}

Business.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only business days.
Business.Name: Business

Calendar.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes all calendar days.
Calendar.Name: Calendar

CommodityBusiness.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only commodity business days.
CommodityBusiness.Name: CommodityBusiness

CurrencyBusiness.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only currency business days.
CurrencyBusiness.Name: CurrencyBusiness

ExchangeBusiness.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only stock exchange business days.
ExchangeBusiness.Name: ExchangeBusiness

ScheduledTradingDay.Doc: When calculating the number of days between two dates the count includes only scheduled trading days.
ScheduledTradingDay.Name: ScheduledTradingDay
